race.comment: PERFECTLY PROPER (8) is stakes placed and was within range in Group company in her two starts last preparation. Owns a Lark Hill trial win and Pikes' booking suggests she's pleasing. Maps well and is well-placed to win. NICCIANA (1) led here beaten a whisker on debut and returns to the race track with a Lark Hill trial win under the saddle. CJP stays aboard and expect him to be further improved. ACORN (2) debuts and just missed in a recent Lark Hill trial with Pike on. Faithfull rides today and he maps well enough. Looks ready to race well. INTOXICATING (9) resumes and will carry just 51.5kgs with the claim. Was good on debut and in the first of her two lead-up trials. Worth a look.
